SUMMARY:A Boogie Wit da Hoodie at Simon Skjodt Assembly Hall
DESCRIPTION:Platinum Entertainment Group and The Touring company are exci
 ted to present the highly-anticipated return of the Bronx-bred hip-hop ar
 tist A Boogie Wit da Hoodie live at Simon Skjodt Assembly Hall on Saturda
 y\, April 11. This show promises to be an unforgettable night of hip-hop 
 and entertainment.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Platinum Entertainment Group and The To
 uring company are excited to present the highly-anticipated return of the
  Bronx-bred hip-hop artist A Boogie Wit da Hoodie live at Simon Skjodt As
 sembly Hall on Saturday\, April 11. This show promises to be an unforgett
 able night of hip-hop and entertainment.</p>
